---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <h1>Best Missoula</h1>

  <p>
    Welcome to the hub of five valleys — home of the Montana Grizzlies,
    the University of Montana, and the Missoula Paddleheads. Missoula
    sits where the Bitterroot, Blackfoot, and Clark Fork Rivers all
    come together, and it's one of the best small cities in the
    country for getting outside, eating well, and settling in for a
    while.
  </p>

  <p>
    Looking for a fishing guide near Missoula? Start here. We've built
    a real comparison tool covering guided fishing outfitters across
    the region — filter by water, fishing type, region, and price to
    find the right trip, plus straightforward guides on how to pick a
    guide and the best time of year to go.
  </p>

  <div class="cta-row">
    <a href="/outdoors/fishing/" class="btn btn-primary">Explore fishing guides</a>
    <a href="/outdoors/fishing/compare-outfitters/" class="btn btn-secondary">Compare outfitters</a>
  </div>

  <p>
    <a href="/eat/">Eat</a> ·
    <a href="/stay/">Stay</a> ·
    <a href="/do/">Do</a> ·
    <a href="/outdoors/" class="nav-outdoors">Outdoors →</a>
  </p>
</Layout>

<style>
  .cta-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    background: #2f4538;
    color: #faf8f4;
  }
</style>